{"tid":370721,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】Telegram 香港突發事故報料區 Group","createTime":"2017-08-23T07:37:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-23T09:35:22.000Z","uid":1542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1d29dd76e926559172f2ee91c17b91cd506770c7","tid":370721,"uid":1542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:37:31.000Z","msg":"香港突發事故報料區 :<a href=\"https://t.me/hknow\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhknow&d=MZbb6wOW8NUOP6KiUv6%2B8MPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=18ec5719\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hknow</a><br />\n<br />\n本Group歡迎所有在香港境內的突發事故消息通報。<br />\n<br />\n本Group發現有版友在本區貼上一些不是突發性質的貼文，為增加各版友的可閱性及維持本區的突發報料性質，各管理員一旦發現有內文不屬突發報料性質的貼文，會即時刪除而不作另行通知及事先提醒。<br />\n<br />\n另請大家分享網上資訊時，留意是否突發事故。因為轉發他人資訊時，可能已經是多日前，或多年前的事。那時就不太好了, 如果發現, 會即時刪除。 謝謝大家。<br />\n<br />\n為你搜羅第一手突發資訊<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hknow\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhknow&d=MZbb6wOW8NUOP6KiUv6%2B8MPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=18ec5719\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hknow</a>"},{"pid":"8307c9efddb6915368dcab41c60882c1d7360905","tid":370721,"uid":87704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:46:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56b1aa2b74130e8b9f9220d3a4cae5ee23d15eca","tid":370721,"uid":1542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:46:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85804127fc8d3ed75f301bf311c75a616b66298d","tid":370721,"uid":1542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T09:35:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}